---
title: Cheesy Plant-Based Mince Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa
description: Smokey, cheesy, and packed with flavour, these quesadillas are a total crowd-pleaser! Stuffed with saucy, spiced veggie mince and melty cheese, then crisped to golden perfection, they’re pure comfort with a twist. On the side? A bright, zesty charred corn salsa that brings the perfect pop of sweetness and crunch. Get ready for a hands-on, flavour-loaded fiesta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b2af8ca27a53fcaa21ea40-48bdfaf8.jpeg
